{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YLKudQW8qW437KCwQh9TYa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The CockroachDB is running in `--insecure` mode with `--http-addr=0.0.0.0:8080`. This means:\n1. The DB Console (port 8080) serves plain HTTP (not HTTPS)\n2. SQL (port 26257) is also in insecure mode\n\nSo for the Ingress:\n- The backend protocol for port 8080 is HTTP (not HTTPS), so no special `backend-protocol` annotation needed\n- nginx-ingress will do TLS termination and forward to HTTP 8080\n\nNow let me plan:\nI need to create an Ingress resource in the cockroachdb namespace for the DB Console, pointing to `crdb-ui.example.com` with TLS using the existing secret, routing to the service on port 8080. For the SQL port, I'll set up a TCP proxy by creating a ConfigMap in the ingress-nginx namespace that maps port 26257 to the CockroachDB service.\n\nNow I'm setting up the implementation: creating the ConfigMap, updating the ingress-nginx controller deployment to reference it, and patching the controller service to expose port 26257.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1462,"cache_read_input_tokens":30408,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1462},"output_tokens":26,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a45e8e7c-ca4c-41ce-bfa2-78938f93f14a","uuid":"c1fb2564-346c-404a-a52a-97ad1eec300f","request_id":"req_011CcRAxHRc2BaG7PfdKFQpR"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YLKudQW8qW437KCwQh9TYa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good. CockroachDB is running in insecure mode with plain HTTP on port 8080 and TCP SQL on port 26257. The TLS secret `crdb-ui-tls` already exists. Here's the plan:\n\n1. Create an Ingress for HTTPS → HTTP:8080 (DB Console)\n2. Create a `tcp-services` ConfigMap and wire it into ingress-nginx for port 26257\n\n**Step 1: Create the Ingress for the DB Console**"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1462,"cache_read_input_tokens":30408,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1462},"output_tokens":26,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a45e8e7c-ca4c-41ce-bfa2-78938f93f14a","uuid":"df1bb86c-5d21-459c-b1a8-9523d628c2ef","request_id":"req_011CcRAxHRc2BaG7PfdKFQpR"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YLKudQW8qW437KCwQh9TYa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01YHLx7Sc9uRR1P2L9BqCTbJ","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"kubectl apply -f - <<'EOF'\napiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Ingress\nmetadata:\n  name: crdb-ui\n  namespace: cockroachdb\n  annotations:\n    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/ssl-redirect: \"true\"\nspec:\n  ingressClassName: nginx\n  tls:\n    - hosts:\n        - crdb-ui.example.com\n      secretName: crdb-ui-tls\n  rules:\n    - host: crdb-ui.example.com\n      http:\n        paths:\n          - path: /\n            pathType: Prefix\n            backend:\n              service:\n                name: crdb-cluster-public\n                port:\n                  number: 8080\nEOF","description":"Create Ingress for CockroachDB DB Console"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1462,"cache_read_input_tokens":30408,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1462},"output_tokens":26,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a45e8e7c-ca4c-41ce-bfa2-78938f93f14a","uuid":"32723dc9-8160-4d01-8922-b94e5d482a4c","request_id":"req_011CcRAxHRc2BaG7PfdKFQpR"}
